msgid "Done"
msgstr "Eginda"

msgid "Take Book"
msgstr "Liburua hartu"

msgid "Lectern"
msgstr "Atrila"

msgid "Lecterns not only look good, but are job site blocks for Librarians."
msgstr ""
"Atrilek itxura ona izateaz gain, liburuzainentzako lan-blokeak ere badira."

msgid "Place the Lectern on a solid node for best results. May attract villagers, so it's best to place outside of where you call 'home'."
msgstr ""
"Jarri atrila nodo solido batean emaitza hobeak lortzeko. Baserritarrak "
"erakar ditzake, eta, beraz, hobe da zure 'etxea' den lekutik kanpo jartzea."
